        <title>백준 디스코드 봇 &#39;백준봇&#39;</title>
        <link>https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/</link>
        <pubDate>Tue, 03 Jan 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-1.png" alt="Featured image of post 백준 디스코드 봇 &#39;백준봇&#39;" /&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;백준-디스코드-봇-백준봇&#34;&gt;백준 디스코드 봇 &amp;lsquo;백준봇&amp;rsquo;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;백준 스터디를 진행할 때 문제를 조금 더 이쁘게 올려 보고 싶어 만들었습니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-1.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1187&#34;
	height=&#34;904&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-1_hu3ba0e11ccd78cd419cf9cf4dfafe4b05_113858_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-1_hu3ba0e11ccd78cd419cf9cf4dfafe4b05_113858_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;131&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;315px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://solvedac.github.io/unofficial-documentation/#/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;solved.ac 비공식 API&lt;/a&gt; 를 사용하여 만들었습니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-2.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1500&#34;
	height=&#34;500&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-2_hua3f398f3dc87c7c8d5a4fd5322b217a0_123732_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-2_hua3f398f3dc87c7c8d5a4fd5322b217a0_123732_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;300&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;720px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;사용-방법&#34;&gt;사용 방법&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;문제-올리기&#34;&gt;문제 올리기&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;/백준 문제번호&lt;/code&gt;  로 문제를 올릴 수 있습니다.
&lt;img src=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-6.png&#34;
	width=&#34;962&#34;
	height=&#34;81&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-6_hu2facb2ba88d2dbba0ca32a6b9c440ab0_3694_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-6_hu2facb2ba88d2dbba0ca32a6b9c440ab0_3694_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;1187&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;2850px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;또는 &lt;code&gt;/백준 문제링크&lt;/code&gt;  로 문제를 올릴 수 있습니다.
&lt;img src=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-7.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1121&#34;
	height=&#34;97&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-7_hu0f6723ab47112f2b9c890bf47ad2c7cd_7752_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-7_hu0f6723ab47112f2b9c890bf47ad2c7cd_7752_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;1155&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;2773px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;문제와-소스코드를-함께-올리기&#34;&gt;문제와 소스코드를 함께 올리기&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;/백준 문제번호&lt;/code&gt;  또는 &lt;code&gt;/백준 문제링크&lt;/code&gt;  하단에 소스코드를 같이 입력하면, 문제와 소스코드를 함께 올릴 수 있습니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;줄바꿈은 &lt;code&gt;Shift&lt;/code&gt; + &lt;code&gt;Enter&lt;/code&gt; 키를 눌러주시면 됩니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-4.png&#34;
	width=&#34;964&#34;
	height=&#34;517&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-4_hu95272da1a80a9eb9e31f98224bb7d4be_32035_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-4_hu95272da1a80a9eb9e31f98224bb7d4be_32035_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;186&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;447px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;위 사진과 같이 디스코드의 코드 블럭을 이용하시면, 하이라이팅된 코드를 업로드 할 수 있습니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-3.png&#34;
	width=&#34;970&#34;
	height=&#34;587&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-3_hu42b54d877be7b417125bc335b2754ff6_54257_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-3_hu42b54d877be7b417125bc335b2754ff6_54257_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;165&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;396px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;소스-코드가-길-때&#34;&gt;소스 코드가 길 때&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;디스코드의 Embed의 내용은 4096자 제한이 있습니다.
따라서 Embed의 범위를 벗어나면 아래 사진과 같이 출력합니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-8.png&#34;
	width=&#34;959&#34;
	height=&#34;590&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-8_hu2df989813509d31de0633370673ec202_51433_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-8_hu2df989813509d31de0633370673ec202_51433_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;162&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;390px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;명령어 입력이 잘못된 경우,
&amp;ldquo;잘못된 입력입니다.&amp;rdquo; 라는 메세지를 출력합니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-5.png&#34;
	width=&#34;959&#34;
	height=&#34;590&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-5_hu2df989813509d31de0633370673ec202_51433_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-5_hu2df989813509d31de0633370673ec202_51433_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;162&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;390px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Embed에 실패하여 메세지를 보내지 못한 경우, 또는 solved.ac 서버가 불안정하여 데이터를 가져오지 못한 경우
&amp;ldquo;메세지 전송이 실패했습니다.&amp;rdquo; 라는 메세지를 출력합니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-9.png&#34;
	width=&#34;960&#34;
	height=&#34;69&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-9_hu48de6d47a3ff341ae85709b5d734bb5b_10853_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://gyeongminn.github.io/p/baekjoonbot/image-9_hu48de6d47a3ff341ae85709b5d734bb5b_10853_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;1391&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;3339px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;백준봇-초대하기&#34;&gt;백준봇 초대하기&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://discord.com/api/oauth2/authorize?client_id=1055791861572325417&amp;amp;permissions=17179879424&amp;amp;scope=bot&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;초대 링크&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;현재 너무 바빠 업데이트를 못 하고 있는데, 추후 다양한 기능을 업데이트할 예정입니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
</description>
